<h2 id="using-meta">Using meta</h2>

<p>This element should be used when metadata needs to be visible to the user, for example to display:</p>
<ul>
  <li>the publication date of a page or article</li>
  <li>a category or taxonomy of a page or document</li>
  <li>the name of an author</li>
</ul>

<p>The meta element shouldnâ€™t be used as a <a href="headings">heading</a> or to style <a href="paragraph">paragraph text</a>.</p>
